Package org.hibernate.query.named

Interface NamedObjectRepository

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NamedObjectRepositoryImpl
    public interface NamedObjectRepository
    Repository for references to named things related with queries. This includes named HQL, JPAQL, native and procedure queries as well as named result-set mappings
